extends ProxyLookup
    A Lookup that caches the results of successful lookups performed by another instance.

    • Constructor Detail

      • CachedLookup

        public CachedLookup(Lookup nestedLookup,
                    Integer maxEntries,
                    Scheduler resetSchedule)
        Creates a new CachedLookup.
        Parameters:
        nestedLookup - the underlying lookup to use for cache misses.
        maxEntries - the maximum number of results to cache or null if there should be no limit.
        resetSchedule - the scheduler used to clear/remove all cached entries or null if the cache should never be cleared.
